  <entry>
    <title>数据库第二周笔记</title>
    <url>/2022/03/03/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%91%A8%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2><span id="sql函数">SQL函数</span></h2>
<h3><span id="字符型函数">字符型函数</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>RPAD和LPAD</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 靠左/右对齐</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> lpad(ename,<span class="number">10</span>,<span class="string">' '</span>),sal <span class="keyword">from</span> emp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302220036481.png" alt="image-20220302220036481">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302220036481</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> rpad(ename,<span class="number">10</span>,<span class="string">'.'</span>)<span class="operator">||</span>sal <span class="keyword">from</span> emp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302220107942.png" alt="image-20220302220107942">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302220107942</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>LOWER,UPPER和INITCAP
<ul>
<li>lower：全变小写</li>
<li>upper：全大写</li>
<li>INITCAP：第一个变大写，其他不变</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p>​ 大小写转换</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> initcap(<span class="built_in">lower</span>(ename)),sal <span class="keyword">from</span> emp;	</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302220131159.png" alt="image-20220302220131159">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302220131159</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li><p>LENGTH &amp; SUBSTR</p>
<p>列出名字最后一个字母</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> ename,substr(ename,length(ename),<span class="number">1</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> emp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li>
<li><p>LTRIM和RTRIM</p></li>
</ul>
<p>​ 左/右截断函数，从左/右开始检查，直到检查到不符合则停止</p>
<p>形式借用，建立虚表</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">*</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302220709071.png" alt="image-20220302220709071">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302220709071</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> ltrim(<span class="string">'abcdefg'</span>,<span class="string">'badg'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302170126473.png" alt="image-20220302170126473">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302170126473</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>​ 右截断一般用于去除右端空格</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> rtrim(<span class="string">'abcde    '</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302170431661.png" alt="image-20220302170431661">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302170431661</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>INSTR</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 从左边数去，第一次找到的位置</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> instr(<span class="string">'ababababababbab'</span>,<span class="string">'ba'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302170519000.png" alt="image-20220302170519000">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302170519000</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>CHR</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 查找ASCII码</p>
<ul>
<li>REPLACE</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 替代函数</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> replace(<span class="string">'abbsihdsljxansd'</span>,<span class="string">'a'</span>,<span class="string">'1'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302220908733.png" alt="image-20220302220908733">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302220908733</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>TRANSLATE</li>
</ul>
<p>​ REPLACE高级版，对应替换</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">translate</span>(<span class="string">'abbsihdsljxansd'</span>,<span class="string">'abs'</span>,<span class="string">'123'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302221042013.png" alt="image-20220302221042013">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221042013</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>SOUNDEX</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 读音函数，可用于模糊语音查询(不支持英语s)</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">*</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> emp <span class="keyword">where</span> soundex(ename) <span class="operator">=</span> soundex(<span class="string">'skot'</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302171022657.png" alt="image-20220302171021995">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302171021995</figcaption>
</figure>
<h3><span id="数值型函数">数值型函数</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>NVL</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 封装NULL函数,指定NULL为0或其他值</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> ename , sal,comm,nvl(comm,<span class="number">0</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> emp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302171223432.png" alt="image-20220302171223432">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302171223432</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>CEIL</li>
</ul>
<p>天花板函数，返回比输入要打的最小整数</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">ceil</span>(<span class="number">4.756</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302171343015.png" alt="image-20220302171343015">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302171343015</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">ceil</span>(<span class="number">-4.756</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302171404226.png" alt="image-20220302171404226">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302171404226</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>FLOOR</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 地板函数，与CELLIL相反</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">FLOOR</span>(<span class="number">4.756</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302221203865.png" alt="image-20220302221203865">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221203865</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">FLOOR</span>(<span class="number">-4.756</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302221225801.png" alt="image-20220302221225801">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221225801</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>ROUND</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 四舍五入</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> ROUND(<span class="number">4.756</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="C:\Users\Terry\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220302221309965.png" alt="image-20220302221309965">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221309965</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> ROUND(<span class="number">4.456</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302221332395.png" alt="image-20220302221332395">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221332395</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>trunc</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 规定小数位输出，直接截断。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> trunc(<span class="number">4.456</span>,<span class="number">2</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302221441901.png" alt="image-20220302221441901">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221441901</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>GREATEST</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 选出最大值</p>
<ul>
<li>TO_CHAR</li>
</ul>
<p>格式化输出，把不是字符串的东西变成字符串，后面为格式码。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> to_char(<span class="number">12.3456</span>,<span class="string">'9999.999'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302221614652.png" alt="image-20220302221614652">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221614652</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> to_char(<span class="number">12.3456</span>,<span class="string">'0099.999'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302221647785.png" alt="image-20220302221647785">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221647785</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> to_char(<span class="number">12.3456</span>,<span class="string">'$0099.999'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302221728683.png" alt="image-20220302221728683">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221728683</figcaption>
</figure>
<h3><span id="日期函数">日期函数</span></h3>
<p>​ 一般缺省时间为12：00：00</p>
<ul>
<li>TO_CHAR</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> ename,to_char(hiredate,<span class="string">'yyyy-mm-dd'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> emp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302221901572.png" alt="image-20220302221901572">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221901572</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> ename,to_char(hiredate,<span class="string">'yyyy-mm-dd hh:mi:ss'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> emp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302221953920.png" alt="image-20220302221953920">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302221953920</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>SYSDATE</li>
</ul>
<p>伪装函数(<code>SYSDATE</code>,<code>USER</code>,<code>ROWNUM</code>,<code>ROWID</code>,<code>LEVEL</code>)一种，获取当前日期</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> sysdate <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302222106146.png" alt="image-20220302222106146">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302222106146</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>​ 修改输出样式</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> to_char(sysdate,<span class="string">'yyyy"年"fmmm"月"dd"日"'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302175451433.png" alt="image-20220302175451433">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302175451433</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>TO_DATE</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 常用于<code>INSERT</code>语句</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> to_date(<span class="string">'20010101111111'</span>,<span class="string">'yyyymmddhhmiss'</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220303000205409.png" alt="image-20220303000205409">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220303000205409</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>ADD_MONTHS</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 增加一个月</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> add_months(sysdate,<span class="number">3</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220303000351752.png" alt="image-20220303000351752">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220303000351752</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>LAST_DAY</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> last_day(sysdate) <span class="keyword">from</span> dual;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220303000502887.png" alt="image-20220303000502887">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220303000502887</figcaption>
</figure>
<ul>
<li>MONTHS_BETWEEN</li>
</ul>
<p>​ 计算两个日期相隔多少个月(考试题)</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> ename,trunc(months_between(sysdate,hiredate)<span class="operator">/</span><span class="number">12</span>) <span class="keyword">from</span> emp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220302180257163.png" alt="image-20220302180257163">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220302180257163</figcaption>
</figure>
]]></content>
