  <entry>
    <title>数据库第二周练习</title>
    <url>/2022/02/26/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%91%A8%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2><span id="环境变量设置">环境变量设置</span></h2>
<ol type="1">
<li><p>将<code>SQLPLUS</code>提示符改为<code>SQL=</code></p>
<p>在<code>sqlplus</code>中输入命令：</p></li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> sqlprompt "SQL="</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225142139201.png" alt="image-20220225142139201">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220225142139201</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>​ 若要实现永久修改，需要在<code>shell</code>中输入命令</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim $ORACLE_HOME/sqlplus/admin/glogin.sql</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225142237991.png" alt="·">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">·</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>​ 在其中加入</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> sqlprompt "SQL="</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<p>​ 即可实现永久修改。</p>
<ol start="2" type="1">
<li>去掉输出结果的列头</li>
</ol>
<p>​ 在<code>sqlplus</code>中输入</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> heading off</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225142617923.png" alt="image-20220225142617923">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220225142617923</figcaption>
</figure>
<h2><span id="sql语句练习"><code>SQL</code>语句练习</span></h2>
<ol type="1">
<li>列出工资在 2000-3000 之间（包括临界值）并且没有提成的员工</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">*</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> emp <span class="keyword">where</span> SAL <span class="keyword">between</span> <span class="number">2000</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="number">3000</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> COMM <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">NULL</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225143205349.png" alt="image-20220225143205349">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220225143205349</figcaption>
</figure>
<ol start="2" type="1">
<li>列出和 JONES 同一部门的员工名字</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> ENAME <span class="keyword">from</span> emp <span class="keyword">where</span> DEPTNO <span class="operator">=</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> DEPTNO <span class="keyword">from</span> emp <span class="keyword">where</span> ENAME <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">'JONES'</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225144126767.png" alt="image-20220225144126767">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220225144126767</figcaption>
</figure>
<ol start="3" type="1">
<li>列出名字以 S 开头，名字长度为 5 个字符的员工</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">*</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> emp <span class="keyword">where</span> ENAME <span class="keyword">like</span> <span class="string">'S%'</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> LENGTH(ENAME)<span class="operator">=</span><span class="number">5</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225145136237.png" alt="image-20220225145136237">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220225145136237</figcaption>
</figure>
<ol start="4" type="1">
<li>列出在芝加哥工作的员工，并且按工资从高到低排列</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">*</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> emp <span class="keyword">where</span> (DEPTNO <span class="operator">=</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> DEPTNO <span class="keyword">from</span> dept <span class="keyword">where</span> LOC <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">'CHICAGO'</span>)) <span class="keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> SAL <span class="keyword">desc</span> ;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225145955750.png" alt="image-20220225145955750">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220225145955750</figcaption>
</figure>
<ol start="5" type="1">
<li>列出姓名以 J 开头，总收入超过 2500 的员工名字</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> ENAME <span class="keyword">from</span> emp <span class="keyword">where</span> ENAME <span class="keyword">like</span> <span class="string">'J%'</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> ((SAL<span class="operator">+</span>COMM)<span class="operator">&gt;</span><span class="number">2500</span> <span class="keyword">or</span> (SAL<span class="operator">&gt;</span><span class="number">2500</span>));</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225151231327.png" alt="image-20220225151231327">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220225151231327</figcaption>
</figure>
<h2><span id="模拟数据导入sql">模拟数据导入SQL</span></h2>
<p>​ 用自己熟悉的编程语言（包括并不限于 C++，R，Python
等等），产生一个包含 500 万行
数据的文本文件，每行由两个列组成，第一列是随机产生的长度为 10
字符的字符串，第二 列是随机产生的 8
位数字，两列中间用空格分开（如下）</p>
<p>abfgerjhgg 64758741</p>
<p>awqwyiuusa 10987622</p>
<h2><span id="模拟数据">模拟数据</span></h2>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="keyword">as</span> pd</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> random</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> string</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> tqdm <span class="keyword">import</span> tqdm</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">num  = <span class="number">5000000</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">f = <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">"simuhw2.txt"</span>, <span class="string">'w'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> tqdm(<span class="built_in">range</span>(num)):</span><br><span class="line">    temp_num  = <span class="string">''</span>.join(random.sample(string.digits, <span class="number">8</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    temp_char = <span class="string">''</span>.join(random.sample(string.ascii_lowercase, <span class="number">10</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    temp_simu = temp_char + <span class="string">" "</span> + temp_num</span><br><span class="line">    f.writelines(temp_simu)</span><br><span class="line">    f.write(<span class="string">'\n'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">f.close()</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<ol type="1">
<li>建表</li>
</ol>
<p>​ 名字为simuhw2，列名为name和id</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="keyword">TABLE</span> simuhw2(name varchar2(<span class="number">10</span>),id number(<span class="number">8</span>));</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<ol start="2" type="1">
<li>构建文档</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi simuhw2.ctl</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225224242587.png" alt="image-20220225224242587">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220225224242587</figcaption>
</figure>
<ol start="3" type="1">
<li>导入文件</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sqlldr userid=scott/tiger control=simuhw2.ctl log=simuhw2.log </span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225173651225.png" alt="image-20220225173651225">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220225173651225</figcaption>
</figure>
<ol start="5" type="1">
<li>查看数据</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="built_in">COUNT</span>(<span class="operator">*</span>) <span class="keyword">FROM</span> simuhw2;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225173915923.png" alt="image-20220225173915923">
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20220225173915923</figcaption>
</figure>
